    "content": "<p>Identify the products $$A$$ and $$B$$ in the reactions :</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{aligned}\n& R-X+\\mathrm{AgCN} \\longrightarrow A+\\mathrm{Ag} X \\\\\n& R-X+\\mathrm{KCN} \\longrightarrow B+\\mathrm{KX}\n\\end{aligned}$$</p>",
