    ],
    "answer": null,
    "explanation": "<p>Hinsberg reagent is $$\\mathrm{C}_6 \\mathrm{H}_5 \\mathrm{SO}_2 \\mathrm{Cl}$$, (benzene sulphonyl chloride) which is used for detection and confirmation of primary, secondary and tertiary amines.</p>",
